---
layout: base.njk
description: A research project on self-learning and best educational practices — across computer programming, systems design, foreign languages, linguistics, and history — powered by machine learning (ML) and large and small language models (LLM, SLM).
---
<section class="intro">
  <div class="intro-logo">
    <img src="/img/Bemigotik.jpg" alt="a hand drawn Bemigot mascot — a capital letter B with small ears, an eye, mouth and the right nostril. Looks like a curious hippo.">
  </div>
  <div class="intro-text">
    <h1>Bemigot</h1>
    <p>
      A research project focused on self-learning and best educational
      practices, particularly in the fields of
      <em>computer programming</em>, <em>systems design</em>,
      <em>foreign languages</em>, <em>linguistics</em>, and <em>history</em>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Learning <em>Machine Learning</em> and <em>Language Models</em> (Large
      and Small) rejuvenated the project at the dawn of 2025 — a fitting loop
      for a project about learning — and Bemigot hopes to ride this wave for
      the foreseeable future.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

{% if collections.posts.length %}
<section class="recent">
  <h2>Latest writing</h2>
  <ul class="post-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts | head(3) %}
    <li>
      <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | isoDate }}</time>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  <p class="more"><a href="/blog/">All posts →</a></p>
</section>
{% endif %}
